 :theory: n. The consensus, idea, plan, story, or set of rules that is
currently being used to inform a behavior. This usage is a generalization and
(deliberate) abuse of the technical meaning. "What's the theory on fixing
this TECO loss?" "What's the theory on dinner tonight?" ("Chinatown, I
guess.") "What's the current theory on letting lusers on during the day?"
"The theory behind this change is to fix the following well-known screw...."